    <item>
      <title>Milei将削减7万个国家工作岗位，吹嘘电锯紧缩政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/milei-to-cut-70-000-state-jobs-boasting-of-chainsaw-austerity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱计划在未来几个月解雇 7 万名政府工作人员，这是迄今为止最明显的迹象之一，表明自由主义者的电锯式做法打算如何削减肿胀的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/milei-to-cut-70-000-state-jobs-boasting-of-chainsaw-austerity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 23:39:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
